data.description: Location! Location! Location! Within minutes of historic downtown Winter Garden, Great schools, next to Winter Garden Village and several stores and restaurants. Located minutes from SR 429 and SR 50. NEW ROOF 2019!!! SOLAR SYSTEM INSTALLED IN 2021, energy savings. 6 person hot tub, fence, etc. The master bedroom is huge with a large sitting area and spacious walk-in closet. Enjoy time with the family in the oversized loft/game room! The bedrooms are all a good size, with one downstairs for family visits! Enjoy the privacy and additional space with a corner lot. New AC Handler installed in and systems fully changed for optimal performance! Close to the walkway to go to the lake, park, pool, tennis courts and playground! All part of your community! Come and see this house just minutes from downtown Winter Garden, highways, shopping and restaurants. Don't let this opportunity slip away!    The future buyer will have to take over and transfer in its name with the Corning Credit Union bank 216 fixed installments of $ 228.17 for the solar system installed in 2021.
